source.data:
Feature: Login page

    Feature Login page will work depending on the user credentials.

    Background:
        Given A user opens a saucelabs website
    Scenario: Success Login
        When A user enters the username "standard_user"
        And A user enters the password "secret_sauce"
        And A user clicks on the login button
        Then the url will contains the inventory subdirectory
    Scenario: Blocked Login
        When A user enters the username "locked_out_user"
        And A user enters the password "secret_sauce"
        And A user clicks on the login button
        Then The error message "Epic sadface: Sorry, this user has been locked out." is displayed
    Scenario: Incorrect Username Login
        When A user provides incorrect credentials
            | username | password     |
            | testName | secret_sauce |
        And A user clicks on the login button
        Then The error message "Epic sadface: Username and password do not match any user in this service" is displayed
    Scenario: Incorrect Password Login
        When A user provides incorrect credentials
            | username      | password     |
            | standard_user | testPassword |
        And A user clicks on the login button
        Then The error message "Epic sadface: Username and password do not match any user in this service" is displayed

Feature: Join page

    Feature Login page will work depending on the user credentials.

    Background:
        Given user opens myer website

    Scenario: Success Create Account
        When user verifies they are on "Join" page
        Then user clicks on join button
        When user inputs details
        | email | firstname | lastname | mobilenumber | dateofbirth | address | addressfinderval |
        |       |           |           |               |           |           |                   |
        Then user clicks on create account
        And user they are on "Account" page

    Scenario: Incorrect Email Validation
        Then user verifies they are on "Join" page
        Then user inputs email address ""
        Then user verifies "email" error message with text ""
        When user verifies they are on "Join" page


    Scenario: Incorrect Password Validation
        Then user verifies they are on "Join" page
        Then user inputs email address ""
        Then user inputs password ""
        Then user verifies "password" error message with text ""
        When user verifies they are on "Join" page

    Scenario: Incorrect Mobile Number Validation
         Then user verifies they are on "Join" page
        Then user inputs email address ""
        Then user inputs password ""
        Then user verifies "mobile number" error message with text ""
        When user verifies they are on "Join" page

    Scenario: Incorrect Date of Birth Validation
        Then user verifies they are on "Join" page
        Then user inputs email address ""
        Then user inputs password ""
        Then user verifies "dateofbirth" error message with text ""
        When user verifies they are on "Join" page

    Scenario: Incorrect Address Validation
        Then user verifies they are on "Join" page
        Then user inputs email address ""
        Then user inputs password ""
        Then user verifies "address" error message with text ""
        When user verifies they are on "Join" page


    Scenario: Empty Form Validation
         Then user verifies they are on "Join" page
        Then user clicks on create account
        And user they are on "Account" page
        Then user verifies "email" error message with text ""
        When user verifies they are on "Join" page

    #Scenario: Success Create Account with Manual Address
